These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, designer, scientist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, june, december
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall, tiparillo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, reggae
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the designer##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
3. the scientist is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the cain-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
6. the scientist is the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Job      | scientist  | librarian       | designer   |
| Birthday          | december | may | june |
| Cigar         | cain  | tiparillo | pall-mall    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | blues       | folk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lilac, purple
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, palace
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, soy-milk
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, snake
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the snake is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Color          | fuchsia      | lilac  | purple        |
| House         | palace | gothic-revival | farmhouse |
| Beverage   | coffee | almond-milk | soy-milk       |
| Pet           | snake     | rat     | hedgehog      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, zinnia, tulip
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, dancer, software-developer
3 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, rat
House: victorian, cottage, craftsman
1. the software-developer is the victorian house##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Flower      | zinnia    | marigold        | tulip |
| Job           | dancer    | software-developer | chef    |
| Pet   | pony | rat             | rabbit  |
| House     | craftsman     | victorian                | cottage  |

