.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, magic-tricks
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, lawyer
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, aquamarine, ebony
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person who likes green is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby          | board-games    | magic-tricks  | rock-climbing      |
| Job           | lawyer    | analyst | fisherman |
| Color   | ebony   | aquamarine  | green     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | snake    | lizard      |

