.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
City: marseilles, edinburgh, berlin
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, malaysian, polish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bluemaster, fonseca
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, lizard
1. the havana-smoker is the malaysian##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the polish is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is the italian##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| City         | berlin | marseilles     | edinburgh   |
| Nationality           | polish       | malaysian   | italian     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster     | havana | fonseca |
| Pet           | lizard      | dog         | hedgehog  |

