The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the game-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Birthday          | march | october       | january |
| Hobby   | fishing     | board-games       | skydiving   |
| Cigar           | dunhill      | game       | chaman     |
| Sport         | sailing   | snowboarding | tennis  |

