.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, cola
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, mechanic, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, disaster
There are 3 different nationalities: british, malaysian, italian
1. the italian is in the middle##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking coffee is the malaysian##1
4. the accountant is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the software-developer is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage       | coffee            | hot-chocolate      | cola  |
| Job         | software-developer | accountant | mechanic |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary               | disaster | adventure |
| Nationality   | malaysian             | italian       | british      |

