.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
City: edinburgh, berlin, boston
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, davidoff, vegafina
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, snowboarding
3 different pets are kept: bird, goat, lizard
1. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| City           | boston | edinburgh         | berlin |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | davidoff | vegafina     |
| Sport   | volleyball   | parkour       | snowboarding     |
| Pet           | lizard    | goat         | bird        |

