.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, whist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, folk, gospel
House: victorian, colonial, townhouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, helicopter
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the victorian house is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Game           | go | whist | mah-jongg |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | folk       | reggae     |
| House   | colonial     | townhouse         | victorian     |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus          | boat      |

