The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, february, september
3 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, domino
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, horse
1. the owner of the horse is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | aconite    | azalea | daffodil |
| Birthday   | february | october     | september     |
| Game   | domino        | mah-jongg        | backgammon        |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | horse         | hamster     |

