.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, water
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, mexican
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, blood-red, red
3 different games are played: bridge, domino, billiard
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes lavender##1
3. the mexican is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person drinking water is the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing domino is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage    | coffee | sprite     | water      |
| Nationality        | chinese | nigerian       | mexican |
| Color       | blood-red | lavender | red  |
| Game   | domino    | bridge   | billiard  |

