City: liverpool, hannover, miami
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, blood-red, apricot
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, gospel, salsa
1. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to miami is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower      | rose | amaryllis | begonia       |
| City          | miami     | liverpool   | hannover       |
| Color         | grey  | apricot   | blood-red |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | salsa       | classical  |

