.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, baking, rock-climbing
3 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, hedgehog
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, action
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, punk
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing      | baking    | writing    |
| Pet          | hedgehog         | rabbit    | frog   |
| Movie-Genre           | spy | action | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | punk         | d&b     | folk    |

