3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, siglo, montecristo
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Game      | mah-jongg  | whist   | monopoly  |
| Pet          | snake   | hedgehog | pony   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | disco      | rock    |
| Cigar   | siglo | baccarat    | montecristo |

