.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, fuchsia
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, fuchsiacher
There 3 different types of food: pepper, apricot, lemon
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, april
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the fuchsiacher is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person eating apricot is the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Color      | chestnut         | fuchsia     | orange     |
| Job           | lawyer        | fuchsiacher | journalist |
| Food   | apricot        | lemon   | pepper    |
| Birthday         | april | march   | june |

