.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, potato, tomato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
City: venice, new-york, edinburgh
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, pilot, dressmaker
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the nurse is on the far left##1
5. the pilot is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | tomato     | potato    | avocado    |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | sprite | lemonade     |
| City   | venice  | new-york      | edinburgh        |
| Job         | nurse   | pilot   | dressmaker |

 